---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken & Haloumi Burger with Oven-Baked Fries & Lemon Aioli
description: These burgers are jam-packed with delicious flavours, from the juicy Portuguese-style chicken and haloumi to the creamy lemon
aioli and sweet caramelised onion. You'll never settle for a takeaway burger again!
